Polish: per-note Gaussian jitter σ=3 ms on melodic, 1 ms on ostinato, 0 ms on grid-locked machine voices. (~3h)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-*Subtotal: ~27 hours*\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+*Subtotal: ~30 hours*\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+### Sprint 2: Quality Scoring\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+**Depends on:** Sprint 0 (Versioning System), Sprint 1 (Quality Scoring)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+- **T-011** [T1] Implement R12 Sensor-to-Intent Aggregation Matrix: smoothed IIR + hysteresis → aggregate intentions (global_energy, global_restraint, global_brightness). (~3h) → deps: T-001\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+- **T-012** [T1] Implement bounded reactive delta track in scheduler with per-parameter modulation caps. (~3h) → deps: T-001\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+- **T-013** [T1] Expose aggregate-intention telemetry (global_energy/restraint/brightness) in operator diagnostics, never raw one-to-one mappings. (~3h) → deps: T-001\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+- **T-014** [T1] Build the metric battery: IOI CoV, velocity σ, DNVR/DNODR, pitch-class entropy H1, Grooving Similarity (GS), tempo autocorrelation ρ₁, LZ76 compression ratio, novelty peaks per phrase, silence-at-phrase-boundaries. (~3h) → deps: T-001\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+- **T-015** [T1] Build anti-pattern tests: quantization ghosting, dynamic compression, motif ossification, random-as-expression (Ljung-Box), symmetric-arc uncanny, dead-silence failure. (~3h) → deps: T-001\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+- **T-016** [T1] Implement performance-worm logger: 2D trajectory in tempo–loudness space + convex-hull area computation as CI artifact. (~3h) → deps: T-001\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+- **T-017** [T1] Integrate metric battery + anti-pattern detectors into CI gate with fail-on-regression policy. (~3h) → deps: T-001\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+- **T-018** [T1] Embed rule-stack provenance in exported audio metadata (e.g., WAV iXML chunk or sidecar JSON) for listener-review workflow. (~3h) → deps: T-001\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+*Subtotal: ~24 hours*\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n 