iety so not every phrase uses a symmetric parabola: per-phrase random selection from parabolic/cosine/asymmetric-Bezier/flat/inverted with peak-position variance. (~3h) → deps: T-011\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+- **T-028** [T1] Implement restraint parameter enforced as global dampener across rules. (~3h) → deps: T-011\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-*Subtotal: ~9 hours*\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+*Subtotal: ~30 hours*\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n ### Sprint 5: Library & CRUD Polish\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-**Depends on:** Sprint 0 (Versioning System), Sprint 1 (Improvement Engine Hardening)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+**Depends on:** Sprint 0 (Versioning System), Sprint 1 (Quality Scoring)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-- **T-013** [T1] Create a production-course knowledge base that the composer can consult at runtime. (~3h) → deps: T-001\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-- **T-014** [T1] Implement a verified pitch, interval, scale, and mode library. (~3h) → deps: T-001\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-- **T-015** [T1] Add chord construction and voicing support. (~3h) → deps: T-001\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-- **T-016** [T1] Encode functional harmony and modulation strategies. (~3h) → deps: T-001\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-- **T-017** [T1] Expand rhythm, meter, groove, and time handling. (~3h) → deps: T-001\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-- **T-018** [T1] Add counterpoint and linear voice-combination rules. (~3h) → deps: T-001\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-- **T-019** [T1] Build a synthesis-architecture strategy registry. (~3h) → deps: T-001\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-- **T-020** [T1] Add production-aware frequency allocation and EQ policy. (~3h) → deps: T-001\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+- **T-029** [T1] Implement the Event dataclass with score-level, performance-level, reactive-delta, and provenance fields. (~3h) → deps: T-001\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+- **T-030** [T1] Implement PerformanceIntent per-phrase metadata with arc shape, deviation bounds, tension target, restraint, and call/response role. (~3h) → deps: T-001\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+- **T-031** [T1] Implement SectionEnvelope with breakpoint functions over tempo_base, density_target, dynamic_plane, brightness, tension_trajectory. (~3h) → deps: T-001\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+- **T-032** [T1] Define IntentTag enum (build/settle/question/answer/withhold/punctuate) and require every phrase to carry one. (~3h) → deps: T-001\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+- **T-033** [T1] Define Role enum (ostinato/melody/pad/perc/accent/silence) with grid_locked flag and role-filter policy used by all rules. (~3h) → deps: T-001\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+- **T-034** [T1] Implement seeded-RNG architecture with per-stage sub-seeds derived from a root seed along a seed_path tuple. (~3h) → deps: T-001\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+- **T-035** [T1] Refactor composition stage to emit score-tree with PerformanceIntent + SectionEnvelope + IntentTag metadata, deterministic from composition seed. (~3h) → deps: T-001\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+- **T-036** [T1] Define the OSC/SuperCollider event contract that carries full Event metadata including rule_stack provenance through to the synth. (~3h) → deps: T-001\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+- **T-037** [T1] Build a deterministic replay harness that reproduces any past performance from (score, composition_seed, interpretation_seed, delta_track). (~3h) → deps: T-001\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-*Subtotal: ~24 hours*\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+*Subtotal: ~27 hours*\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n ### Sprint 6: Stretch Goals\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n **Depends on:** Sprint 0 (Versioning System)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-- **T-021** [T2] Add post-tonal, spectral, and microtonal material strategies. (~6h)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-- **T-022** [T2] Build SuperCollider recipe references without coupling tests to live audio. (~6h)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-- **T-023** [T2] Add course-driven self-critique and revision targets. (~6h)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-- **T-024** [T2] Turn the production course into executable curriculum exercises. (~6h)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n-- **T-025** [T2] Add operator diagnostics for production-course decisions. (~6h)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n+- **T